{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"struct","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckbox","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckbox"}],"modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Structure","title":"OUDSCheckbox","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents12OUDSCheckboxV"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layout to add in your views a lonely checkbox, without labels, texts nor icons components."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use a checkbox with additional texts and icon, prefer instead "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/init(isOn:accessibilityLabel:isError:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","generated":true},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/body"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/View-Implementations"],"anchor":"Default-Implementations","generated":true}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckbox","ki